: 0, "select": 0, "author": 741508}, {"id": 107810, "content": "分手后庆祝自己拜托了烂人去庆祝", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443026}, {"id": 107811, "content": "分手，要回所有一切送他的东东，只赚不赔！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698221}, {"id": 107812, "content": "分手后庆祝自己摆脱了烂人去庆祝", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443026}, {"id": 108068, "content": "这些问题我都没资格回答/(ㄒoㄒ)/~~我还是先找个男朋友吧........", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717567}, {"id": 107813, "content": "拼命看电影看演出把自己丢进几十分钟或者一整天别人的生活，或者去旅行", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 42503}, {"id": 107814, "content": "一直钱都是为她花，现在分手了一个人可以买很多自己喜欢的东西。觉得至少得对自己好点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 233, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682517}, {"id": 107815, "content": "还没分呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 107816, "content": "愿天下有情人终成眷属。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 107817, "content": "分手炮，开房的钱，买套的钱，打车的钱，最后晚餐的钱，感觉钱包身体和灵魂被掏空。", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698239}, {"id": 107818, "content": "买烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715843}, {"id": 107819, "content": "没对象的我怎么回答这个问题？?", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419840}, {"id": 107820, "content": "分手了我会尽量避免独处，一个人会更难受。跟朋友一起至于花多少钱肯定比宅家里多很多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715740}, {"id": 107821, "content": "喝酒，KTV，和朋友一起嗨皮，放纵自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715846}, {"id": 107822, "content": "难分，我那么爱她，她也是。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713726}, {"id": 107824, "content": "其实是全给自己买买买想买就买 以前还担心钱不够 单身了 又啥不够的呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 687682}, {"id": 107825, "content": "感觉分不坨了，因为没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715857}, {"id": 108083, "content": "感觉自己一个人花钱绝对比恋爱少，皮艾斯，我还是个女的，醉了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717711}, {"id": 107829, "content": "踏上独自一人的散心之旅，只为暂时离开这个有她的城市。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333612}, {"id": 108853, "content": "对自己好点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722669}, {"id": 107830, "content": "所以题图是在嘲讽单身狗么", "image": null, "praise_count": 161, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 298191}, {"id": 108086, "content": "改改改改改", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610564}, {"id": 107831, "content": "搬家", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632137}, {"id": 107832, "content": "喝酒，玩耍，购物", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623377}, {"id": 109112, "content": "分手后在异地，只为再见他一面，买了不打折的机票", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724342}, {"id": 107833, "content": "借我的钱不用还了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667615}, {"id": 108091, "content": "买饮料，早餐，衣服，化妆品，给男朋友买买买很开心～所以还没分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162244}, {"id": 107836, "content": "散伙饭，开房钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683507}, {"id": 108604, "content": "流量费??分手了到处找知乎论坛，分手了之后如何走出来??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721055}, {"id": 107837, "content": "买买买以此治愈失恋！", "image": "img/option/option/20160815121559350odOjEx4SV8PRQ.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 563538}, {"id": 107838, "content": "一个短信吧，廉价么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 111849}, {"id": 107839, "content": "散伙饭", "image": n